// EXPECT: 5
// ADR-0057: scalar Outcome value-merge through `if`. The merge result is an
// Outcome StackSlot; `Statement::Assign` now moves the whole slot word-by-word
// (was 1-word → "OutcomeDiscriminant on non-Outcome local"). Positive arm.
function f(n: Integer) -> Integer~Integer = if n == 0 { ~+ 5 } else { ~- -1 }
function main() -> Integer = match f(0) { ~+ x => x  ~- e => e }
